    <title>Login</title>
</head>
<body>
    
<div class="sidenav">
    <div class="login-main-text">
       <h2>Application<br> Registeration Page</h2>
       <p>Login from here to access.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="login-main-text">
        <h5>Nasscom Project<br> Created By: Ashu Goyal, Virat Singh Chauhan<br>
